{"tid":108932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"共產黨員禁止獲得美國綠卡和入籍美國（禁止移民）!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2017-02-05T15:18:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-08T02:20:05.000Z","uid":22675,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"742eaed534b9c25415b09006e30f7dae6926e7e8","tid":108932,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T15:18:24.000Z","msg":"長島律師Kevin<br />\n今天 11:18<br />\n<br />\n很多人私信，統一回答下：<br />\n<br />\n1. 共產黨移民美國那個案例為什麼不見啦？我也不知道。根據你國法律法規據，內容不予顯示，我可以看到。<br />\n<br />\n2. 據美國移民法 Immigration And Nationality Acts (INA) &sect;212(a)(3)(D)(i)的規定，<span style=\"color: red;\">過去10年內是共產黨員身份的，禁止獲得美國綠卡和入籍美國（禁止移民）</span>，但黨員身份不影響非移民類簽證申請。<br />\n<br />\n3. 其它相關美國法律問題，就PM。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://wx3.sinaimg.cn/mw690/006yVqyXgy1fcff9kor4nj31ai0j4q90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwx3.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F006yVqyXgy1fcff9kor4nj31ai0j4q90.jpg&h=ac96640d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\ncopy from 新浪微博.<br />\n<img src=\"http://wx1.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/419e93begy1fcf9stv5uxj20qo1beag4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwx1.sinaimg.cn%2Fbmiddle%2F419e93begy1fcf9stv5uxj20qo1beag4.jpg&h=12f092a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e86b59898014c3e0db029fac7fefd8591164a495","tid":108932,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T15:50:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c72bf2c255b64e2bedfa3ced310cd1751d2f4502","tid":108932,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T15:52:08.000Z","msg":"咁易啦<br />\n打個電話俾法輪功退黨保平安咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41e981bc91b5425f55665f7f44ca65d4057f50ff","tid":108932,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T15:54:14.000Z","msg":"拉晒返去中國打靶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d540b9df1a536c57b6c472e6dcb4e9c86ea3c